Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

Lei lines deep beneath the earths surface have been dormant for eons. But now, as the world is on the brink of extinction, these lines are starting to pulse with the power of the ancient gods. The mana is rising through the lei lines to the earths surface and the few humans who can tap into it are becoming the last hope for the survival of the human race.

She can feel the power of the earth flowing through her. But what to do with it?
